Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:02.67,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.18,0:00:05.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我突然有一種不祥的可怕預感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:09.88,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}劇場 {\1c&H000000&}其十一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:14.67,Petit,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}劇場{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}⑾{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}那個{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}跟{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}那個{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}跟(以下略){\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}一起{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}結帳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.23,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 能拜託你把這些都買下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.43,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:16.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是菜月昴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:18.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,無知蒙昧 天下不滅的窮光蛋是也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.70,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,出口就在那邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,對不起是我錯了 其實我身上還是帶了錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:26.01,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就這麼說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:27.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一開始就料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:31.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不過你一開始就說得這麼直接 就算是我也會被嚇倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:34.29,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,因為我這不推銷東西怎麼做買賣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.96,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你想買什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,就是普通的過來買瓶可樂而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:41.00,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也很喜歡碳酸飲料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:44.07,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,那種熟食跟碳酸飲料一起吃下去的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.43,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,簡直沒有比這更棒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:46.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.52,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在買熟食還有10％優惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 那給我來份炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.65,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷告訴你一個秘密 熟食跟飯糰一起買的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.58,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,優惠30円哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:03.03,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,哦說起來飯糰 推薦你這個新品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:05.76,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一直都在努力進貨 但是總是很快就賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的是很好運很好運 恰好留了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:10.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,好好 這個我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:12.92,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,還有 要是在店裡消費800円以上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以抽獎喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:18.04,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,一般人我不告訴 特別容易中獎 不抽的話可是很虧的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是應該再補上一包玉米小棒棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.34,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,酸酸的東西再配上甜食的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:24.83,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,美味簡直無法抵擋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:26.38,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,所以不然再來份冰淇淋怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超級好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:28.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,買買買！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:31.79,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,這個啦 這個啦 那個啦 那些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:34.24,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,總計十萬円
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.77,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,自己選好要買的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:40.82,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,最後卻不付錢的話我們可是很困擾的 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說 我也沒有這麼多錢啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:45.70,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的便利商店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,又來了個麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.12,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,凡夫俗子居然在狂妄地買買買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那個我回過神來就已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.86,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,我們店可都是好東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:58.85,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,越是識貨的人買的越多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.56,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.88,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,姑且就當被你的花言巧語慫恿一次好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:06.52,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,這家店的所有東西都賣給妾身好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,全部！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.57,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.56,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,車子跟侍女們就在門外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘快裝好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.36,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.02,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,好好 馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:17.01,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟小兄弟你讓開點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.71,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,欸 商品？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.99,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經沒有東西剩下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.11,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,都讓這位公主大人給買走了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:24.49,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我買瓶可樂...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:27.42,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,連我的存在都...
